extends layout

block content
  p welcome to the main index page. This view demonstrates PUG rendering, variable injection, and template iteration.
  
  h2 Iterating Collections in Pug
  p Below is a list of dynamic items passed directly from the Express controller and rendered using the Pug <code>each item in data</code> loop.
  
  .list-container
    each item in data
      .list-item
        .bullet
        span= item
